title: Famous Men of Modern Times
creator: John H. Haaren and A.B. Poland
description: LibriVox recording of Famous Men of Modern Times, by John H. Haaren and A.B. Poland. Famous Men of Modern Times is a series of biographical sketches written for the purpose of making the study of history lively and interesting by giving insight into the men who lived during this time. Summary by Laura Caldwell For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover, or other languages or formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.
